law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 187, Part II, sec. 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 4189-4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Reports on corporations by Secretary of State to Department of Revenue; notice and forms to be given corporations.
